Introduction

CoCo is a children’s girl group under Fancy Factory. The members of the group trained under Choomseory Dance Academy & Art Company. The first group of girls debuted on January 28, 2019, with their single “Talk Talk.” In 2020, they debuted for the second time with new members through the single "Be Quiet". On June 29, 2021, CoCo announced that their contracts with all the current lineup members were terminated and that they have revamped their SNS accounts to include the 'Coco Mademoiselle' dance team, some of whom will become official members of the next generation of CoCo.
